            <sentence>
                <offset>0</offset>
                <text>This Egyptian 5-year-old boy (III.1) was the first child to this family.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>73</offset>
                <text>A younger sister (Patient 2) was similarly affected (Fig. 1), and another younger brother was healthy.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>176</offset>
                <text>He was born at term after an uneventful pregnancy.</text>
            </sentence>
