            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>482</offset>
                <text>On examination at that age, his weight, height, and head circumference were 15 kg (−1.6 SD), 97.2 cm (−2.4 SD), and 51.3 cm (mean), respectively.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>628</offset>
                <text>Upper/lower segment ratio was 1.5 and arm span was 89 cm.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
