            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1195</offset>
                <text>Ophthalmologic evaluation (using indirect ophthalmoscope and slit lamp) showed normal lens, vitreous and fundus and normal visual acuity.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1333</offset>
                <text>No abnormalities were found during the routine laboratory investigations (complete blood picture, thyroid hormone profile).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1457</offset>
                <text>Metabolic screening and chromosomal examination from peripheral blood lymphocytes were normal.</text>
            </sentence>
